<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Blessed be Yahweh</para>

<para style="q1">because he has heard the sound of my pleading!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Yahweh is my strength and my shield;</para>

<para style="q1">my heart trusts in him, and I am helped.</para>

<para style="q1">Therefore my heart greatly rejoices,</para>

<para style="q1">and I will praise him with singing.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Yahweh is the strength of his people,</para>

<para style="q1">and he is the saving refuge of his anointed one.</para>
